org.springframework.cloud.dataflow.server.repository

Class JdbcDataflowJobExecutionDao

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.cloud.dataflow.server.repository.JdbcDataflowJobExecutionDao
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataflowJobExecutionDao

    public class JdbcDataflowJobExecutionDao
extends Object
implements DataflowJobExecutionDao
    Stores job execution information to a JDBC DataSource. Mirrors the JdbcJobExecutionDao but contains Spring Cloud Data Flow specific operations. This functionality might be migrated to Spring Batch itself eventually.
    Author:
    Gunnar Hillert, Corneil du Plessis
